title: Power user suddenly permanently banned
text: I’ve only posted a few videos but used TikTok to get updates from news accounts I follow. Then one day I was logged out, and when I tried to log back in I got an error message saying I was permanently banned. No reason why, no warnings, no explanation. Glad I didn’t invest more time or energy in my account, when they can just block you out and keep your content.
